{"tid":1364231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然我好驚...","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:34:47.000Z","uid":278491,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33bbe488e7bc558b7e210ff260e1c93635931998","tid":1364231,"uid":278491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"每一次發夢我都只係企後面支援下<br />\n自己乜裝備都無<br />\n又好驚比人捉<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔止係一名公務員<br />\n我係一名紀律部隊人員<br />\n連3年試用期都未過既廢柴<br />\n<br />\n今次散播哂消息話會掟野<br />\n身為女仔又好驚毀容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我決定今次要著哂裝備<br />\n因為著上制服我係為市民服務<br />\n除左制服我更加要著裝備為自己同香港人奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望你地唔會嫌我拖累大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">27/7 15:30 元朗見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b54507141430b41d51a333b5e5d36ac3802f456","tid":1364231,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:15:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f33299f46e7dd27177f8970f5e61a750e1de9100","tid":1364231,"uid":201853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"886a7f5fe5dd595cb272cde6977cb5bff489d300","tid":1364231,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"到時見，今次必須去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a44d58110eb8c28d2267f669eb9575635746f5","tid":1364231,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbd7d2826e38b0f952b965634669ff0746bca09","tid":1364231,"uid":44181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"點都要出，唔可以留低勇武"}]}